HEADWORD: Septennate
<hw>Sep*ten"nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>septennat</ets>.]</ety> <def>A period of seven years; <as>as, the
<ex>septennate</ex> during which the President of the French Republic
holds office</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Septennial</ent>⟦br⟧
